        <td>Marc yes po, Marc no po, Ordered, Reject</td>
        <td>Use Temporary hold status to hold orders for quesons/other actions.</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

    <h4>MARC record download</h4>
    <p>Orders with a workflow state of <i>MARC queue yes po</i> or <i>MARC queue no po</i> will be processed into MARC records for loading into Sierra. Click <i>Download MARC</i> button on the index page to generate two separate MARC files: one for print PO and one for no print PO. Use the respective loaders in Sierra to input the records.</p>
